Monsters have returned. They’ve thrown the battlefield into darkness. The question now is: will you fight against them … or alongside them? Find out what kind of beast you are in DARK REALM, the latest season of World of Tanks Modern Armor! 

Step to the shadows for a Halloween-inspired season and earn frightfully good rewards across 100 stages, including War Chests, Gold, and Premium tanks. Enter the DARK REALM, starting October 7 on PlayStation!
